title: DDFP 388: Week 2 review & DDFP All-Stars
itunes:title: DDFP 388: Week 2 review & DDFP All-Stars
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank to discuss Monday Night Football and the prime candidates for the final “DDFP All-Stars” roster. Ike Taylor and Maurice Jones-Drew then join the show to recap the biggest storylines from Week 2 of the NFL season.
